engagement of-- it's the active

34
00:01:48,790 --> 00:01:52,000
engagement of all the
stakeholders with the system,

35
00:01:52,000 --> 00:01:54,490
between the time when
it starts to operate--

36
00:01:54,490 --> 00:01:56,020
