80
00:03:43,390 --> 00:03:45,820
which we also call repair.

81
00:03:45,820 --> 00:03:49,920
Dealing with small and large
failures, recalls, anomalies.

82
00:03:49,920 --> 00:03:52,030
This is a big deal in
the automotive industry,

83
00:03:52,030 --> 00:03:53,440
as we know.

84
00:03:53,440 --> 00:03:55,540
Increasingly
protecting the system

85
00:03:55,540 --> 00:03:58,480
from either random
or targeted attacks.

86
00:03:58,480 --> 00:04:03,380
Cyber, physical, right,
physical security but also cyber

87
00:04:03,380 --> 00:04:06,430
security is becoming
