The space shuttle had a 10 year
design life, roughly from 1971

200
00:09:19,650 --> 00:09:21,750
until '81, first flight.

201
00:09:21,750 --> 00:09:25,020
And then we operated
the shuttle for 30 years

202
00:09:25,020 --> 00:09:28,710
